Summary: 5 or 6 transparent bubbles, w/ an inner light sour
divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in an old drive-in movie theatre parking lot.When, all ofa sudden, I observed 4-6 bubbles(transparent) with an inner light source wereoverhead and coming closer to me... and thats all I remember about theexperience... After the experience a few days later, I noticed two incisions inmy genital area. And, theyre still present to this day...Never having themchecked out by a doctor...Im really wondering what the hell they are. If you oranyone else known have any idea what they are...Please contact me.For years Ihave thought that Im going crazy...because, I cant recall the time loss or thestrange incisions...thank you for reading about this...And, please guide me toanyone, besides the government, to help me to learn about what has happened tome.
